public interface OperationStates
OperationStates
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     OperationStates operationStates = OperationStates.builder()
             .processing(1)
             .validationFailed(1)
             .unresolved(1)
             .waitForMasterVariant(1)
             .imported(1)
             .rejected(1)
             .build()
